<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">頌古</cb:mulu>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B488.0314c" n="0314c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="3"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="3"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="3"><cb:jhead>斗南暐禪師語錄卷之下</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c02"/><byline cb:type="other">侍者法權記錄</byline>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">偈</cb:mulu><head>偈</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">眼耳鼻舌身意</cb:mulu><head>眼耳鼻舌身意<note place="inline">六首</note></head>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c05"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0314c0501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">晝夜交輝朗太虛明如日月照無私瞎驢滅<anchor xml:id="beg_20" type="cb-app"/>卻<anchor xml:id="end_20"/>年前
<lb ed="J" n="0314c06"/>事宇宙茫茫幾箇知</l></lg>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c07"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0314c0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">四維上下悉皆聞一擊忘知喪膽魂霹靂聲中消息
<lb ed="J" n="0314c08"/>盡從斯塞斷是非門</l></lg>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c09"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0314c0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">面門獨露一孤峰玉洞無私兩道通臭去香來瞞不
<lb ed="J" n="0314c10"/>得但將矢橛振宗風</l></lg>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c11"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0314c1101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">銅唇鐵舌解談空遍覆三千不記功七七九年無一
<lb ed="J" n="0314c12"/>字至今狼籍海龍宮</l></lg>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c13"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0314c1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">煙霞洞裏陪雞犬荊棘林中作主人長臥白雲閒作
<lb ed="J" n="0314c14"/>夢驢胎馬腹億分身</l></lg>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c15"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0314c1501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">癩馬枯椿事莫期瞻之前後播鎗旂太平本是將軍
<lb ed="J" n="0314c16"/>定倒弄橫拈任意騎</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">四威儀</cb:mulu><head>四威儀</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c18"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0314c1801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">山中行花鳥無心自作吟相識知音天下少三生石
<lb ed="J" n="0314c19"/>上舊時人</l></lg>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c20"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0314c2001" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">山中住挂角羚羊無影樹白日木雞醒醒啼金烏下
<lb ed="J" n="0314c21"/>兔追風去</l></lg>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c22"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0314c2201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">山中坐慈愍利名人兩箇但把紅塵早脫身莫嫌老
<lb ed="J" n="0314c23"/>衲袈裟破</l></lg>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c24"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0314c2401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">山中臥流水溪邊幾夢過石洞草深常入定翻身忘
<lb ed="J" n="0314c25"/><anchor xml:id="beg_21" type="cb-app"/>卻<anchor xml:id="end_21"/>來時路</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c26"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">題石女夫人</cb:mulu><head>題石女夫人</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c27"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0314c2701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">此女從來不嫁君如何喚作石夫人梳粧月鏡星簾
<lb ed="J" n="0314c28"/>下赤體穿衣挂白雲</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c29"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">題淡和尚</cb:mulu><head>題淡和尚</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0314c30"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0314c3001" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">者箇和尚千了百當佛法世法雙收雙放筆走龍蛇
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B488.0315a" n="0315a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a01"/>真箇人天榜樣</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">室中禮懺有感</cb:mulu><head>室中禮懺有感</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a03"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">謾說微塵劫數多生前培植苦娑婆要知末後真消
<lb ed="J" n="0315a04"/>息彼岸何曾隔海波</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">採柏子</cb:mulu><head>採柏子</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a06"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">開花結子正初冬採落銀花露雪容粉骨碎身輸敵
<lb ed="J" n="0315a07"/>手從教光奪日頭紅</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">老僧崖</cb:mulu><head>老僧崖</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a09"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">圓顱方服僧儀全何代遊來住此巔一念不生渾是
<lb ed="J" n="0315a10"/>定逢人不解口談禪</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">誦經</cb:mulu><head>誦經</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a12"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">胸襟流出舌尖頭得意忘言不外求四十九年無一
<lb ed="J" n="0315a13"/>字瞿曇有口也難酬</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示僧</cb:mulu><head>示僧</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a15"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315a1501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">但遇明師是勝緣何須特地遠追攀但能直下翻身
<lb ed="J" n="0315a16"/>去煩惱菩提一体圓</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">看花</cb:mulu><head>看花</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a18"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315a1801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">一園紅白應時開風拂清香撲鼻來幾度倚欄頻翫
<lb ed="J" n="0315a19"/>處月明簾影共徘徊</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a20"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">勸母念佛</cb:mulu><head>勸母念佛</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a21"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315a2101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">子欲歸家有一言菩提不退好心田但能識破多生
<lb ed="J" n="0315a22"/>夢佛母從登上品蓮</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a23"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">考工</cb:mulu><head>考工</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a24"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315a2401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">一粒金丸永不離今朝舉起更無疑幾回爐內翻筋
<lb ed="J" n="0315a25"/>斗者箇何曾有是非</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a26"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示沙彌</cb:mulu><head>示沙彌</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a27"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315a2701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">沙彌來請法與他一耳摑若向掌上會天長并地闊</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a28"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">月下偶成</cb:mulu><head>月下偶成</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315a29"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315a2901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">終日群居別有天隨緣任運自安然箇中消息誰能
<lb ed="J" n="0315a30"/>識明月當空不露言</l></lg></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B488.0315b" n="0315b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">夜聞板聲</cb:mulu><head>夜聞板聲</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b02"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315b0201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">空谷傳聲響似雷更深更下一楗椎虛堂寂靜無人
<lb ed="J" n="0315b03"/>到獨許天心皓月來</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">飛來峰</cb:mulu><head>飛來峰</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b05"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315b0501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">生成體段巧玲瓏特地飛來顯妙容頂上蓮花藏日
<lb ed="J" n="0315b06"/>月週圍千佛繞靈峰</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">參雲林和尚</cb:mulu><head>參雲林和尚</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b08"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315b0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">水漲船高風又來揚帆架櫓出天台梢公力勇船頭
<lb ed="J" n="0315b09"/>硬撞倒雲林老古錐</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">步玉開師原韻</cb:mulu><head>步玉開師原韻</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b11"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315b1101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">碧玉初開漫露蹤粗雕細琢欲成功本來妙體如明
<lb ed="J" n="0315b12"/>得規矩方圓任變通</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">打碎鐘子</cb:mulu><head>打碎鐘子</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b14"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315b1401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">拶碎虛空<g ref="#CB01403">㘞</g>一聲當陽拔出眼中釘通身白汗青天
<lb ed="J" n="0315b15"/>雨杲日重消火裏冰</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示透宗還豫章</cb:mulu><head>示透宗還豫章</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b17"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315b1701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">學道先須透此宗叮嚀此去悟心空忽然吸盡西江
<lb ed="J" n="0315b18"/>水長舌原來在口中</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b19"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">除夕</cb:mulu><head>除夕</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b20"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315b2001" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">東村王老夜燒錢現出紅爐火裏蓮歷劫坦然無變
<lb ed="J" n="0315b21"/>色大家齊唱太平年</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b22"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">拄杖</cb:mulu><head>拄杖</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b23"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315b2301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">秘密深藏萬八峰龍天推出振宗風拈來插向滄溟
<lb ed="J" n="0315b24"/>外掃盡妖狐信不通</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b25"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">爆竹</cb:mulu><head>爆竹</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b26"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315b2601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">親遭毒手幾多回輕易人前口不開時節到來全體
<lb ed="J" n="0315b27"/>用迸山倒嶽發寒灰</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b28"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">贈聞旨道兄</cb:mulu><head>贈聞旨道兄</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315b29"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315b2901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">洞徹無生倒命根一聞千悟是奇入從今更不疑他
<lb ed="J" n="0315b30"/>物滿腹絲綸別有文</l></lg></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B488.0315c" n="0315c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">贈樹文道兄</cb:mulu><head>贈樹文道兄</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c02"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315c0201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">鐘山分袂各東西落葉殘紅恨別離腸斷三更心粉
<lb ed="J" n="0315c03"/>碎不知何日又逢師</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">樹文兄留別</cb:mulu><head>樹文兄留別</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c05"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315c0501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">錫共鐘山寺相談百日期與君分袂去回首意難離</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">茶鐘墮地不碎</cb:mulu><head>茶鐘墮地不碎</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c07"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315c0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">擲地金聲喫一驚一番提起一番新當陽撲出無人
<lb ed="J" n="0315c08"/>識固有天然不壞身</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">和樹文兄原韻</cb:mulu><head>和樹文兄原韻</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c10"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315c1001" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">紫金城畔紫金峰過出人間事不同靈鷲儼然無二
<lb ed="J" n="0315c11"/>處今朝重振舊家風</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">贈香谷師</cb:mulu><head>贈香谷師</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c13"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315c1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">佛法無多識者稀奔南走北枉呈機直饒熟讀三千
<lb ed="J" n="0315c14"/>卷蕩子歸家失路迷</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">化木魚偈</cb:mulu><head>化木魚偈</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c16"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315c1601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">金光爍爍口微開觸著轟轟動地雷一遇知音出隻
<lb ed="J" n="0315c17"/>手大家齊唱法王來</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">贈微笑軒行實賢弟</cb:mulu><head>贈微笑軒行實賢弟</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c19"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315c1901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">微笑軒中一作家金襴傳後隱光華他時格外尋知
<lb ed="J" n="0315c20"/>己拈起靈山不老花</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c21"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">贈妙有關主法師</cb:mulu><head>贈妙有關主法師</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c22"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315c2201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">向上圓關不外通經行坐臥任從容時將一滴曹溪
<lb ed="J" n="0315c23"/>水遍灑天台萬八峰</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c24"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">化齋</cb:mulu><head>化齋</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c25"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315c2501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">初秋夏末到東甌接待無糧不自由雲水都來要飯
<lb ed="J" n="0315c26"/>喫我今權作老金牛</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c27"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">別飛泉法師</cb:mulu><head>別飛泉法師</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c28"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0315c2801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">作偈吟詩話舊交奇言妙句意何超揮毫寫出當年
<lb ed="J" n="0315c29"/>事竹榻篷窗共一宵</l></lg>
<lb ed="J" n="0315c30"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0315c3001">其二</p>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B488.0316a" n="0316a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a01"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316a0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">此際重逢話夙緣溪邊分袂水涓涓九秋暫別他山
<lb ed="J" n="0316a02"/>去萬里瞻風望月圓</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">贈愚若兄掩關</cb:mulu><head>贈愚若兄掩關</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a04"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">大海潮聲日夜喧阿兄求靜隱松源寂然不動無邊
<lb ed="J" n="0316a05"/>際佛祖難窺第一關</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為新大德開淡齋</cb:mulu><head>為新大德開淡齋</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a07"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">留情淡處律精嚴清白甘泉湧舌尖嚼碎莖虀明底
<lb ed="J" n="0316a08"/>事諸方五味不須參</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">贈玉輪朱居士誦經</cb:mulu><head>贈玉輪朱居士誦經</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a10"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316a1001" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">佛法無多說向君持經展卷過平生有時<g ref="#CB01403">㘞</g>地一聲
<lb ed="J" n="0316a11"/>去三世如來把手行</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">贈朱居士遊山</cb:mulu><head>贈朱居士遊山</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a13"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316a1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">太平何事賴人修突兀名區任意遊南北東西無阻
<lb ed="J" n="0316a14"/>礙迴途須用自甘休</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">贈奉先顧居士</cb:mulu><head>贈奉先顧居士</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a16"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316a1601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">世事人情懶去親閒房靜坐樂天真四恩總報無多
<lb ed="J" n="0316a17"/>子宇宙茫茫見一人</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">贈孟入陳居士參禪</cb:mulu><head>贈孟入陳居士參禪</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a19"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316a1901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">道義相交不倦談西來祖意好追參要知向上超玄
<lb ed="J" n="0316a20"/>路剔起眉毛腦後看</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a21"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">步注居士原韻</cb:mulu><head>步注居士原韻</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a22"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316a2201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">玉堂光燦透玄微霹靂聲中不動衣堪笑時人猶不
<lb ed="J" n="0316a23"/>覺誰知目下自生機</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a24"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">示分唇海沙彌</cb:mulu><head>示分唇海沙彌</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a25"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316a2501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">彌勒口開有甚奇不如者箇小沙彌逢人懶說西來
<lb ed="J" n="0316a26"/>意笑破口門兩片皮</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a27"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">搬磚偶成</cb:mulu><head>搬磚偶成</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a28"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316a2801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">拋磚引玉上虛堂凜凜威風不可當萬象森羅齊舉
<lb ed="J" n="0316a29"/>手一家有事百家忙</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316a30"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">水筧</cb:mulu><head>水筧</head>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B488.0316b" n="0316b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b01"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316b0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">萬法囊藏在腹中吞而復吐養蛟龍光吞日月乾坤
<lb ed="J" n="0316b02"/>大一派曹源正脈通</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">遊虎丘口占</cb:mulu><head>遊虎丘口占</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b04"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316b0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">虎丘山上白雲家客到濃煎穀雨茶頑石心空能點
<lb ed="J" n="0316b05"/>首時人徒看眼前花</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">燈下偶成</cb:mulu><head>燈下偶成</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b07"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316b0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">黃金出汁苦心知費盡鉗錘照用時古佛燃燈光世
<lb ed="J" n="0316b08"/>界至今者點不曾移</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">石柱峰</cb:mulu><head>石柱峰</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b10"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316b1001" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">拄地撐天玉柱峰龍門倒插半空中清溪落落衝潮
<lb ed="J" n="0316b11"/>去隔岸騷人信未通</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">登月臺觀瀑</cb:mulu><head>登月臺觀瀑</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b13"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316b1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">瀑布翻空何處來驚天動地吼如雷遠觀一片銀山
<lb ed="J" n="0316b14"/>壁近視珍珠灑月臺</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">坐禪</cb:mulu><head>坐禪</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b16"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316b1601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">磨襠擦褲幾多年喪盡身心不會禪再上蒲團閒作
<lb ed="J" n="0316b17"/>夢何須特地起狼煙</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">舟中阻風作以慰眾</cb:mulu><head>舟中阻風作以慰眾</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b19"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316b1901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">扁舟蕩漾泊琳宮暫爾蒼天鼓逆風自是觀音舒法
<lb ed="J" n="0316b20"/>力管教巽女轉神通一尋柔櫓浮滄海三道輕帆挂
<lb ed="J" n="0316b21"/>碧空千步銀沙親玉趾金仙洞裏見慈容</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b22"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">贈道原法師</cb:mulu><head>贈道原法師</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b23"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316b2301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">道在中原不變遷包含萬象利人天喜君廣有超方
<lb ed="J" n="0316b24"/>作妙喻微言滿大千</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b25"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">搬瓦</cb:mulu><head>搬瓦</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b26"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316b2601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">握土成金上法堂獅兒齊立幾何行爭先頭角翻空
<lb ed="J" n="0316b27"/>舞古殿重增舊日光</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b28"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">慕得然道兄善書畫偶成</cb:mulu><head>慕得然道兄善書畫偶成</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316b29"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0316b2901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">作略君家得自然筆尖纔動化三千丹青點破澄潭
<lb ed="J" n="0316b30"/>月鐵硯磨開長夜天</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B488.0316c" n="0316c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">佛事</cb:mulu><head>佛事</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">地藏開光</cb:mulu><head>地藏開光</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c03"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0316c0301">九華峰頂現金身何似莊嚴色相新者裏一毫能著
<lb ed="J" n="0316c04"/>眼放光無處不稱尊。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">彌勒安位</cb:mulu><head>彌勒安位</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c06"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0316c0601">理法界不動纖塵事法界縱橫自在理事無礙法界
<lb ed="J" n="0316c07"/>重重殿閣崢嶸處處應身化現布袋打開珠回玉轉
<lb ed="J" n="0316c08"/>信手拈來點鐵成金三賢十聖情與無情從地湧出
<lb ed="J" n="0316c09"/>不令而行以拂子打○相云過現未來總不曾離<anchor xml:id="beg_22" type="cb-app"/>卻<anchor xml:id="end_22"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c10"/>者裏又不曾住<anchor xml:id="beg_23" type="cb-app"/>卻<anchor xml:id="end_23"/>者裏大眾且道畢竟在甚麼處擊
<lb ed="J" n="0316c11"/>香几云相逢拍掌呵呵笑天上人間得自由。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">韋馱安位</cb:mulu><head>韋馱安位</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c13"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0316c1301">喝一喝云虛空震動大地輝騰法不孤起令不虛行
<lb ed="J" n="0316c14"/>頂天立地護國安民威靈顯赫古剎重興正當恁麼
<lb ed="J" n="0316c15"/>時一句作麼生殿閣崢嶸新氣象金湯衛護舊家風。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">募天王殿進關</cb:mulu><head>募天王殿進關</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c17"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0316c1701">未遊華藏界先入蝸牛角佛眼覷不破千聖難模索
<lb ed="J" n="0316c18"/>者箇大愚人無參亦無學忽起佛法見將錯與就錯
<lb ed="J" n="0316c19"/>等箇人兒來梵剎興工作即今事若何放下舊蒲團
<lb ed="J" n="0316c20"/>高挂缽囊著。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c21"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">挂梆板</cb:mulu><head>挂梆板</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c22"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0316c2201">師拈槌云鴻鳴輕擊天呼地應金牛喫飯來趙州洗
<lb ed="J" n="0316c23"/>缽去施者受者果因不昧眾中若有彌勒肚皮維摩
<lb ed="J" n="0316c24"/>手段可使斗金日費饑餐飽睡設若五觀未明者裏
<lb ed="J" n="0316c25"/>切須仔細擊梆板云咦。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c26"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">出關</cb:mulu><head>出關</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c27"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0316c2701">閉戶無求活埋此處眨眼三年須臾便過乞我一文
<lb ed="J" n="0316c28"/>功成德聚施者受者必獲如意且道以何為驗驀指
<lb ed="J" n="0316c29"/>櫃云此處無金三十兩。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0316c30"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">剃度師示寂拈香</cb:mulu><head>剃度師示寂拈香</head>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B488.0317a" n="0317a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a01"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317a0101">化身應世唯我本師方外域中化導靡窮某蒙剃度
<lb ed="J" n="0317a02"/>拔濟恩崇思悟別傳于焉西東只期大樹長作帡幪
<lb ed="J" n="0317a03"/>詎料涅槃覿面難逢雖無生滅寧不愴傷音容永隔
<lb ed="J" n="0317a04"/>舍利流光山高水深夕瞻朝望謹具杯茗匍匐登堂
<lb ed="J" n="0317a05"/>師其來格鑒此瓣香。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為母疾割股焚香</cb:mulu><head>為母疾割股焚香</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a07"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317a0701">肉隨刀轉血瀉泉流拆肉還母恩大難酬信手拈來
<lb ed="J" n="0317a08"/>旃檀一片熱向爐中諸佛證鑑然雖如是全身現出
<lb ed="J" n="0317a09"/>尋常事忉利天宮去復回。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a10"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0317a1001">復然頂</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a11"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317a1101">祈母患愈燒身燒臂直下忘軀頂<g ref="#CB00576">𩕳</g>著地。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為火頭僧舉火</cb:mulu><head>為火頭僧舉火</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a13"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317a1301">昔日燒火今被火燒烈燄光中任運逍遙且道功圓
<lb ed="J" n="0317a14"/>行滿事作麼生高聲云放下著。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a15"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0317a1501">入塔</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a16"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317a1601">威音那畔任意縱橫大開門戶全身直入下靈骨云
<lb ed="J" n="0317a17"/>欲識安身立命處會取當陽霹靂聲鳴指一下。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為松崖禪人舉火</cb:mulu><head>為松崖禪人舉火</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a19"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317a1901">重陽九月裏金風遍界吹未曉登高去天明拂袖歸
<lb ed="J" n="0317a20"/>泥牛吼水面海底火星飛無根松樹砍將來置向紅
<lb ed="J" n="0317a21"/>爐燒死灰。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a22"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為無礙禪人舉火</cb:mulu><head>為無礙禪人舉火</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a23"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317a2301">透過金剛圈吞<anchor xml:id="beg_24" type="cb-app"/>卻<anchor xml:id="end_24"/>栗棘蓬通身顯妙用踏破太虛空
<lb ed="J" n="0317a24"/>擲下火炬云日輪不覺沉西去隨身干木徹天紅。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a25"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為雪松沙彌入塔</cb:mulu><head>為雪松沙彌入塔</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a26"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317a2601">冬至月中日風夜風沙飛石走吹倒雪松且道葉落
<lb ed="J" n="0317a27"/>歸根事作麼生近水樓臺先得月向陽花木早逢春。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a28"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為園頭一念舉火</cb:mulu><head>為園頭一念舉火</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317a29"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317a2901">昔年空手把鋤頭今日步行騎水牛撒手到家情念
<lb ed="J" n="0317a30"/>盡更無一物可存留雖然如是且道即今事作麼生
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B488.0317b" n="0317b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b01"/>攛火炬云識得衣中寶翻身迸火星。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為梵音洞佛子捨身舉火</cb:mulu><head>為梵音洞佛子捨身舉火</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b03"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317b0301">清淨法身求善因圓滿報身招惡果百億化身現虛
<lb ed="J" n="0317b04"/>空粉骨碎身超佛祖舉火炬云還見觀音大士麼劫
<lb ed="J" n="0317b05"/>火洞然毫末盡頂門突露一輪紅。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為蓮彰禪師起龕</cb:mulu><head>為蓮彰禪師起龕</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b07"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317b0701">鐵壁銀山萬丈深上天無路地無門從斯透過玄關
<lb ed="J" n="0317b08"/>去天空海闊任縱橫。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b09"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0317b0901">舉火</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b10"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317b1001">昨夜一陣毘嵐風吹倒門前一株松直至樹倒藤枯
<lb ed="J" n="0317b11"/>後更有蓮花火裏紅以火炬打○相云還見麼剔起
<lb ed="J" n="0317b12"/>眉毛腦後看。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b13"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0317b1301">入塔</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b14"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317b1401">舉靈骨云只者箇不在內不在外不在中間且道在
<lb ed="J" n="0317b15"/>甚麼處良久云直下分明說向伊朔風凜凜雨聲微
<lb ed="J" n="0317b16"/>蓮洋浪湧金沙岸斗轉星移月映溪正當恁麼時藏
<lb ed="J" n="0317b17"/>蹤隱跡又作麼生即今放下黃金骨切莫分身兩處
<lb ed="J" n="0317b18"/>看。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b19"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為靈隱禪人起龕</cb:mulu><head>為靈隱禪人起龕</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b20"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317b2001">出入分明不爾欺箇中何更有狐疑但能覷見來時
<lb ed="J" n="0317b21"/>路踏過毘盧任所之。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b22"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0317b2201">舉火</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b23"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317b2301">閃爍靈光透上頭即今毫髮不容留眼睛突出虛空
<lb ed="J" n="0317b24"/>笑燄裏翻身輥火毬。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b25"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0317b2501">入塔</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b26"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317b2601">鳴指一下云空谷傳聲乾坤震應靈光隱隱<anchor xml:id="beg_25" type="cb-app"/>卻<anchor xml:id="end_25"/>是如
<lb ed="J" n="0317b27"/>來真性即今粉骨碎身且向甚處立命者裏欲住便
<lb ed="J" n="0317b28"/>住當定即定塞破牢關聽吾號令復鳴一下。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b29"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為石元禪人起龕</cb:mulu><head>為石元禪人起龕</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317b30"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317b3001">古人休去歇去冷啾啾去一條白練去古廟香爐去
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B488.0317c" n="0317c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c01"/>一念萬年去者漢畢竟向甚麼處去顧視左右云大
<lb ed="J" n="0317c02"/>家送出去。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c03"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0317c0301">舉火</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c04"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317c0401">一向階前灑埽獻花供水忽爾露布踏翻切忌見神
<lb ed="J" n="0317c05"/>見鬼舉火炬云烈燄光中薦取本蹤。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c06"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0317c0601">入塔</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c07"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317c0701">風和日暖桃紅李白趁此水漲船高休待潮落石出
<lb ed="J" n="0317c08"/>正恁麼時樂業成家承誰恩力咄船到橋門自然直
<lb ed="J" n="0317c09"/>便下骨。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為雲水僧起龕</cb:mulu><head>為雲水僧起龕</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c11"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317c1101">遊遍天涯孤峰獨宿踏倒須彌山忘<anchor xml:id="beg_26" type="cb-app"/>卻<anchor xml:id="end_26"/>來時路舉數
<lb ed="J" n="0317c12"/>珠云若向者裏見得無來無去無迷無悟其或未然
<lb ed="J" n="0317c13"/>雨後苔青急須走過。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c14"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0317c1401">舉火</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c15"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317c1501">舉火炬云咄咄水朝東星拱北桃自紅柳自綠魚化
<lb ed="J" n="0317c16"/>龍筍成竹泥牛撞入海山前鹿獨宿急薦主人翁燒
<lb ed="J" n="0317c17"/><anchor xml:id="beg_27" type="cb-app"/>卻<anchor xml:id="end_27"/>娘生屋。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為患毒僧入塔</cb:mulu><head>為患毒僧入塔</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c19"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317c1901">清淨本然異類之質臭氣衝天爛膿滴滴撞著無情
<lb ed="J" n="0317c20"/>漢子拋向紅爐蒸炙鎔作一袋真金果然好箇消息
<lb ed="J" n="0317c21"/>趁此戶牖大開透過銅墻鐵壁。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c22"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為雪如禪人入塔</cb:mulu><head>為雪如禪人入塔</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c23"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317c2301">咄哉雪如吾今問渠本來何面目將甚作真如舉骨
<lb ed="J" n="0317c24"/>襯云言下知端的放下便安居。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c25"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為李氏道人舉火</cb:mulu><head>為李氏道人舉火</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c26"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317c2601">幻寄東甌六十餘秋離鄉別井昨寓明州大士親見
<lb ed="J" n="0317c27"/>到岸忘舟下火云者段光明無間斷滿船空戴月明
<lb ed="J" n="0317c28"/>歸。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c29"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為性空上座入塔</cb:mulu><head>為性空上座入塔</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0317c30"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0317c3001">赤日當空照大千性空空盡體超然悠悠莫論途中
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B488.0318a" n="0318a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a01"/>事且入浮屠仔細看。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為無礙禪人入塔</cb:mulu><head>為無礙禪人入塔</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a03"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0318a0301">咄禪不須參教不須看百年三萬六千朝返覆元來
<lb ed="J" n="0318a04"/>是者漢舉靈骨云還會麼擲地金聲有眼者見正恁
<lb ed="J" n="0318a05"/>麼時符到令行又作麼生夾路桃花風雨後馬蹄何
<lb ed="J" n="0318a06"/>處避殘紅。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為道林上座起龕</cb:mulu><head>為道林上座起龕</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a08"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0318a0801">者箇師僧常演妙音撒手歸家撩起便行向上一路
<lb ed="J" n="0318a09"/>又作麼生喝一喝云驀直去。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為徹凡禪師起龕</cb:mulu><head>為徹凡禪師起龕</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a11"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0318a1101">死中得活活中死去涅槃堂前豈容久住符到奉行
<lb ed="J" n="0318a12"/>路在甚處以手指云這裡去。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為戒全禪師封龕</cb:mulu><head>為戒全禪師封龕</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a14"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0318a1401">門門非別門戶戶還自戶識得箇中人大蟲原是虎
<lb ed="J" n="0318a15"/>不須露爪牙虛空加封鎖。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a16"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0318a1601">起龕</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a17"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0318a1701">指龕云從來寸步不曾離此日當陽說向伊昨夜禪
<lb ed="J" n="0318a18"/>那無影樹秋風颯颯落寒枝時至歸根留不住鐵牛
<lb ed="J" n="0318a19"/>無腳逐雲飛擊龕云起。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a20"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0318a2001">舉火</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a21"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0318a2101">戒全全戒定綱宗振起禪那正脈通長嘯一聲消息
<lb ed="J" n="0318a22"/>盡得處何須更費工昔年換箇破燈盞擲下爐中徹
<lb ed="J" n="0318a23"/>底紅大地秋光都漏泄落霞孤鶩聽西東遂下火。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a24"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為火頭道士起龕</cb:mulu><head>為火頭道士起龕</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a25"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0318a2501">方外得得來聚會學無為纔到選佛場瞥然即便歸
<lb ed="J" n="0318a26"/>心空何處去及第更由誰喝一喝云看腳下。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a27"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0318a2701">舉火</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0318a28"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0318a2801">今朝六月七道人著氣急杲日正當空大千紅燄逼
<lb ed="J" n="0318a29"/>流出汞中金工夫多狼籍阿呵呵識不識薰風自南
<lb ed="J" n="0318a30"/>來為汝通消息遂下火。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B488.0318b" n="0318b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0318b01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">為秋月禪人起龕</cb:mulu><head>為秋月禪人起龕</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0318b02"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0318b0201">來時頭戴中秋月慧鑑胸藏不夜天海外欲行無異
<lb ed="J" n="0318b03"/>路最初一步更為先。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0318b04"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0318b0401">舉火</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0318b05"/><p xml:id="pJ40p0318b0501">生在金陵死在者裏倒斷命根無嗔無喜迥脫根塵
<lb ed="J" n="0318b06"/>投大火聚烈燄光中切須薦取。</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0318b07"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0318b08"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0318b09"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0318b10"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="3"><cb:jhead>斗南暐禪師語錄卷之下終</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
